## How to install ?

```
pip install defineif
```

## How to use it ?

```python
import os

from defineif import DefineIf


class Klass(DefineIf):

    @staticmethod
    @DefineIf(os.name == 'nt')
    def get_platform():
        return 'Windows'

    @staticmethod
    @DefineIf(os.name == 'posix')
    def get_platform():
        return 'Linux'

platform = Klass.get_platform()

print(platform)
```
